room_title: Escape room "Espionage" by Escape Plan Columbia in Columbia
room_description: A spy has been living in Columbia and has enacted a plan to blow up the city. The CIA has enlisted your help to capture the spy, but upon entering the spy’s office, a booby trap has been triggered and you and your friends find yourselves locked inside! You have 60 minutes to find the spy’s computer and deactivate the bomb before our state’s capital is blown to pieces. Can you save the city?
